<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>712</hymn_number>
<title>měi cì de xiāng féng 迦南712</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 měi cì de xiāng féng, xiào róng dōu bǐ cǐ míng kè.
 shì yīn wèi yǒu yé sū, zài nǐ xīn ài zhe wǒ.
 fú yīn bù fēn guó jí, yī dìng yào chuán biàn wàn guó.
 wǒ men shì méng fú de yī dài, shì tiān guó de shǐ zhě.
 gē bì tān shàng de tuó líng shēng, shān gǔ zhōng de yáng míng.
 shèng líng bù duàn de gǎn dòng, cuī cù wǒ men xiàng qián xíng.
 wǎng pǔ tiān xià qù chuán fú yīn gěi wàn mín tīng.
 zhè shì wàn guó de dà shǐ mìng, wàn guó de dà shǐ mìng.</lyrics>
</song>